The detector assembly has been optimized for the prototyping and testing of novel detectors of different size and mass without strict protocols for extremely low radio-purity levels. A rendering together with the final assembly of the Li\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
