The fully assembled detectors were installed at the Northwestern EXperimental Underground site in a Pulse Tube (PT) cooled dilution refrigerator from Cryoconcept. The system is equipped with Cryoconcept’s proprietary Ultra-Quiet Technology™, which uses the \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
